{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/20240403/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"白石研究室"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"bf657c1b-3516-5c1a-b337-4370c272381b","excerpt":"こんにちは。白石です。 今日は大学院の入学式がありました。 履修登録も終えて一旦ひと段落したので、ブログ記事の かさましを兼ねてマークダウンの動作確認を行いたいと思います。 1. はじめに 当ブログではGatsbyJSとgithub-markdown-css…","html":"<p>こんにちは。白石です。</p>\n<p>今日は大学院の入学式がありました。</p>\n<p>履修登録も終えて一旦ひと段落したので、ブログ記事の かさましを兼ねてマークダウンの動作確認を行いたいと思います。</p>\n<h1>1. はじめに</h1>\n<p>当ブログではGatsbyJSとgithub-markdown-cssを使用しています。</p>\n<p>有効なマークダウン記法とその見た目を列挙します。</p>\n<h1>2. 列挙してみる</h1>\n<p>以下，コードとその出力結果を交互に列挙していきます。</p>\n<h1>2.1. ヘッダー</h1>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\"># Header 1\r\n## Header 2\r\n### Header 3\r\n#### Header 4\r\n##### Header 5\r\n###### Header 6</code></pre></div>\n<h1>Header 1</h1>\n<h2>Header 2</h2>\n<h3>Header 3</h3>\n<h4>Header 4</h4>\n<h5>Header 5</h5>\n<h6>Header 6</h6>\n<h1>2.2. サンプルコード</h1>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">```js\r\nconst saltyDuckEgg = \"chinese preserved food product\"\r\n```</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> saltyDuckEgg <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"chinese preserved food product\"</span></code></pre></div>\n<h1>2.3. 表</h1>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"markdown\"><pre class=\"language-markdown\"><code class=\"language-markdown\"><span class=\"token table\"><span class=\"token table-header-row\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">|</span><span class=\"token table-header important\"> Number </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">|</span><span class=\"token table-header important\"> Title                                    </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">|</span><span class=\"token table-header important\"> Year </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">|</span>\r\n</span><span class=\"token table-line\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">|</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">:-----</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">|</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">:---------------------------------------</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">|</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">---:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">|</span>\r\n</span><span class=\"token table-data-rows\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">|</span><span class=\"token table-data\"> 1      </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">|</span><span class=\"token table-data\"> Harry Potter and the Philosopher’s Stone </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">|</span><span class=\"token table-data\"> 2001 </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">|</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">|</span><span class=\"token table-data\"> 2      </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">|</span><span class=\"token table-data\"> Harry Potter and the Chamber of Secrets  </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">|</span><span class=\"token table-data\"> 2002 </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">|</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">|</span><span class=\"token table-data\"> 3      </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">|</span><span class=\"token table-data\"> Harry Potter and the Prisoner of Azkaban </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">|</span><span class=\"token table-data\"> 2004 </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">|</span></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\">Number</th>\n<th align=\"left\">Title</th>\n<th align=\"right\">Year</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">1</td>\n<td align=\"left\">Harry Potter and the Philosopher’s Stone</td>\n<td align=\"right\">2001</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">2</td>\n<td align=\"left\">Harry Potter and the Chamber of Secrets</td>\n<td align=\"right\">2002</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">3</td>\n<td align=\"left\">Harry Potter and the Prisoner of Azkaban</td>\n<td align=\"right\">2004</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h1>2.4. 図</h1>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"markdown\"><pre class=\"language-markdown\"><code class=\"language-markdown\"><span class=\"token url\"><span class=\"token operator\">!</span>[<span class=\"token content\">card</span>](<span class=\"token url\">./card.png</span>)</span>\r\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>img</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">src</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>./profile-pic.png<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/blog/static/63b2a65922010bfe144dd41ab7f4acd0/9c177/card.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 100%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"card\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/blog/static/63b2a65922010bfe144dd41ab7f4acd0/f058b/card.png\"\n        srcset=\"/blog/static/63b2a65922010bfe144dd41ab7f4acd0/c26ae/card.png 158w,\n/blog/static/63b2a65922010bfe144dd41ab7f4acd0/6bdcf/card.png 315w,\n/blog/static/63b2a65922010bfe144dd41ab7f4acd0/f058b/card.png 630w,\n/blog/static/63b2a65922010bfe144dd41ab7f4acd0/9c177/card.png 880w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\r\n<span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/blog/static/f3162a9884461808f78370361dd5d302/0b533/profile-pic.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 100%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"profile pic\" title=\"\" src=\"/blog/static/f3162a9884461808f78370361dd5d302/0b533/profile-pic.png\" srcset=\"/blog/static/f3162a9884461808f78370361dd5d302/c26ae/profile-pic.png 158w,\n/blog/static/f3162a9884461808f78370361dd5d302/6bdcf/profile-pic.png 315w,\n/blog/static/f3162a9884461808f78370361dd5d302/0b533/profile-pic.png 500w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h1>2.5. 数式</h1>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"markdown\"><pre class=\"language-markdown\"><code class=\"language-markdown\">$$ e^{i x} = \\cos{x} + i \\sin{x} $$</code></pre></div>\n<p><span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><msup><mi>e</mi><mrow><mi>i</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow></msup><mo>=</mo><mi>cos</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>i</mi><mi>sin</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">e^{i x} = \\cos{x} + i \\sin{x}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8247em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">e</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8247em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.063em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal mtight\">i</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal mtight\">x</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6667em;vertical-align:-0.0833em;\"></span><span class=\"mop\">cos</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">x</span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">+</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6679em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">i</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mop\">sin</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">x</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<h1>2.6. 文字エフェクト</h1>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"markdown\"><pre class=\"language-markdown\"><code class=\"language-markdown\"><span class=\"token list punctuation\">-</span> <span class=\"token code-snippet code keyword\">`code goes`</span> here in this line\r\n<span class=\"token list punctuation\">-</span> <span class=\"token bold\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">**</span><span class=\"token content\">bold</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">**</span></span> goes here</code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">code goes</code> here in this line</li>\n<li><strong>bold</strong> goes here</li>\n</ul>\n<h1>2.7. 補足用（？）</h1>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"markdown\"><pre class=\"language-markdown\"><code class=\"language-markdown\"><span class=\"token blockquote punctuation\">></span> <span class=\"token list punctuation\">1.</span> This is the first list item.\r\n<span class=\"token blockquote punctuation\">></span> <span class=\"token list punctuation\">2.</span> This is the second list item.\r\n<span class=\"token blockquote punctuation\">></span>\r\n<span class=\"token blockquote punctuation\">></span> Here's some example code:\r\n<span class=\"token blockquote punctuation\">></span>\r\n<span class=\"token blockquote punctuation\">></span>     Markdown.generate();</code></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n<ol>\n<li>This is the first list item.</li>\n<li>This is the second list item.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Here’s some example code:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">Markdown.generate();</code></pre></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h1>3. まとめ</h1>\n<p>マークダウンでブログ投稿ができるのは便利ですね。</p>\n<p>しかし、リストアイテム系が一切表示されないのが気に入らない…</p>\n<p>cssファイルを隅々見て回りましたが、</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">li</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n\t<span class=\"token property\">list-style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> none<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>みたいなのは見当たりませんでした。</p>\n<p>また、数式を中央寄せして数式番号を付与できなかったり、画像のリサイズが効かなかったりと、ブログとして扱うには不便に感じるところが多く見受けられました。</p>\n<p>texの完全下位互換みたいな仕上がりになりますが、自作ブログということで大目に見ていただけると幸いです。</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"マークダウンの動作確認","date":"2024-04-02T22:15","description":"マークダウンの表示結果を自分用に可視化しました。需要は無いです。","tags":["近況報告","ブログ管理"]}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/20240325/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"ブログを立ち上げました"}},"next":null},"pageContext":{"id":"bf657c1b-3516-5c1a-b337-4370c272381b","previousPostId":"ef6b33b6-8145-5e0c-9b9a-bd7e048b306a","nextPostId":null}},"staticQueryHashes":["2268992437","3274528899"],"slicesMap":{}}